The paper discusses a flexible environment for Web data integration, which involves metadata extraction, data source integration, and visualization of integrated data. These topics are closely related to several sub-categories of computer science, including database systems (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), deep learning (cs.DL), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
